address.streetAddress: Allendale II Plan, Gregory Pointe at Deercreek

location.fullValue: Allendale II Plan, Gregory Pointe at Deercreek

data.description: Attractive, 2021 built home situated on #18 tee box of the popular Wyboo Golf Course in the gated community of Deercreek. The kitchen, dining area & family room flow into one another for an open concept, perfect for entertaining & family gatherings. The split floor plan offers plenty of privacy for you & your guests w/ the owner's suite on the main level to the back of the home & two guest bedrooms in the front w/ a bonus room over the garage. The pets will enjoy the spacious backyard already fenced & ready to go!  Relax on the covered patio & enjoy the golf course views or take part in the community amenities which include a swimming pool, library & fitness area.  Close to the lake & numerous boat landings for all your watersport activities. This home has a transferable home warranty.
